=Description=

"Forma’s purpose is to build Solana Economic Zones.

The purpose of a Solana Economic Zone is to build bridges between the Solana economy and Nation’s economies, to help both prosper exponentially.

Over the next 12 months, we are starting with 1-month Solana Economic Zone Assemblies in LaTAM, MEA, APAC & Europe.

After each SEZ Assembly, we will continue our work in host countries to support a wide variety of initiatives - locally & regionally."


